xcuserdata/

## Scripts
*.focusjs
*.focusscript

## Build results
build/
DerivedData/

## Unit-test results
*.xccheckout
*.xcresult

## Bundle index
.index

## Crash reports
*.crash

## Schemes
## Potentially personal schemes
# [v]v/

